{"tid":244423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「怕被渡邊直美吃掉」台灣男星博焱透露斷絕聯絡原因：她太肉慾","createTime":"2017-05-15T12:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T07:21:34.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c60c8b2f319599d555fa3d09cc4cc5ed3c5794e","tid":244423,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"台日混血諧星渡邊直美體重逼近100KG，爽朗又可愛的性格備受粉絲喜愛，曾與台灣演員博焱曖昧中，但4月自爆已經斷了聯絡。近日博焱上節目時揭露斷聯原因，坦言渡邊直美多次熱情邀約，但「怕被她吃掉」才決定不再繼續下去，之後又脫口朋友開他玩笑：「牙一咬就過。」意外掀起網友抨擊，批他人身攻擊。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2520/d2520054.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2520%2Fd2520054.jpg&h=c9dd69aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台男星博焱爆斷聯渡邊直美原因。<br />\n<br />\n博焱8日上《綜藝大熱門》的「自己的料自己爆！」單元，提到和渡邊直美的一段緋聞，透露剛認識的聊天內容都是噓寒問暖，等到時間一久，對方便問他：「什麼時候可以來日本找我？」他反問：「是只有我嗎？」女方則說：「對啊，我可以帶你出去玩。」且前後共邀約了3次，態度相當積極，更可免費獲贈 MazdaShine PLUS 車身鍍膜服務及 IROAD V9 行車記錄儀連前後高清鏡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2520/d2520055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2520%2Fd2520055.jpg&h=05776934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台男星博焱和渡邊直美被傳過緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n對此，博焱表示曾在報導上看過渡邊直美自爆是個「肉慾」的人，擔心如果獨自去日本的話，很有可能會被「吃掉」，連身邊朋友都虧他：「你就為國爭光，犧牲一下，牙一咬就過了。」沒想到這個爆料卻引來部分網友不滿，認為他言語之間帶有人身攻擊，對渡邊直美非常不尊重。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2520/d2520056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2520%2Fd2520056.jpg&h=8bf86ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台男星博焱爆斷聯渡邊直美原因。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，渡邊直美2016年9月曾透過友人認識台灣演員博焱，兩人曾曖昧通一個月line，還曾在節目上視訊，但她2月早已透露兩人斷連絡，自爆「已經斷絕聯絡了，我傳早安給他，他也沒回。」讓這段曖昧情不了了之。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nkc8ewtpR0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNkc8ewtpR0k&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fe27372c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nkc8ewtpR0k</a>"},{"pid":"606edc64a566641e5ec8dbdc3af561b2df216c6e","tid":244423,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"女方則說：「對啊，我可以帶你出去玩。」且前後共邀約了3次，態度相當積極，更可免費獲贈 MazdaShine PLUS 車身鍍膜服務及 IROAD V9 行車記錄儀連前後高清鏡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd73dfcd3dfd9440fa1e32e5f055d93fae8c105","tid":244423,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"張飛搞D咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabe05ad4f8ef549c77982bb952729f460779f49","tid":244423,"uid":6992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"廢咖博焱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b696de3217b98ae6a281b0aff3194f5c61f751","tid":244423,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"個名同樣好熟 諗左勁耐乜水 <br />\n終極三國果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf13575f00eca15d3306c4037b49ad1e52b989","tid":244423,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張飛搞D咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張飛好識食"},{"pid":"00d2634a8f5475fc0d421dbb3e2cdf000b2e8f34","tid":244423,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"其實咁係節目講出黎好撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6906ef96e2041abab1a5f71b0ac54eadacbc9da","tid":244423,"uid":19450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"點解冇朱千雪<img src=\"/asset